Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here it is... Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just enough moisture...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the soil is good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Intruder! I asked who\nyou are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Identify yourself!\N- Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:43.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just have some business\nwith the urn buried here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:47.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once I possess it, I'll leave\nthis sore sight of a village!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So... She knows what's\nburied here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave immediately!\NElse I'll show no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:03:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You talk too much, you stubborn\nignorant old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not\nto interfere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:25.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-that is my sister's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will not let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not a demon like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the demoness,\NUrasue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo's ashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,are now in MY possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...Kagome?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's not...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who bound\nme to the tree!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brought back ugly memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They look alike...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome looks exactly\nlike Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop scaring me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought you were\na scary demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:32.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I punch you just now?\NSorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:34.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nope, not like her at all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not one little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it? I'm getting the\nscent of new blood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold{\i0} it... {\i1}The smell of\nthat blood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why the sudden urge to\ngo back to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm still sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede, you\nmustn't move yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind!\NIt's not a serious wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess not even a flesh wound\nwill keep you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you caught the scent of my blood\non that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, think of your age and\ntake it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:57.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... He wanted to return because\nhe was worried about old Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:02.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This used to be my sister,\NKikyo's gravesite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A grave, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was not strong enough\nto stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I take possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister had unusually strong powers,\neven for a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:30.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If her ashes get into the hands\nof some demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who knows for what evil\npurpose they will be used?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo and I were enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:45.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten who shot an\narrow into my chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard that happened\nfifty years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:06.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha the half-demon wanted\nto take the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and become a full-fledged demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When he came to the village to\ntake the Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the priestess, Kikyo, shot\na sacred arrow which...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}held him fast to a tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:34.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Now that I have this,\NI'll become a real demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in that battle,\NKikyo would lose her life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demoness Urasue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She didn't just steal\NKikyo's ashes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:40.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could smell the dirt from\nthe grave...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is she up to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:03.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you feel sorry for Kikyo,\nthat her grave has been violated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget that you were once\nbitter enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo died long ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:22.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since yesterday, you've been\navoiding looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know! It's because\NI look like Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:35.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why you don't like me,\nright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:39.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:43.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:03.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- what was that just now?\NWhat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Darn! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-you're the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am also a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will take back my sister's ashes\nwith my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, at least tell me in\nwhich direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Urasue is headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you wanna die, old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:36.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'll have to go\nto find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny Kaede, you mustn't!\NYou're in no condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:41.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I hate dealing\nwith old people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get Kikyo's ashes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'll be sure to bring home\nyour bones, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny Kaede, may I come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:07.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's eyes just now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wasn't seeing{\i0} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:19.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was seeing Kikyo\ninside me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll attack tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can smell it...\NShe's not far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:56.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I first saw Inuyasha,\nhe was sleeping, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, he was bound\nto a tree...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But to me, he looked like\nsleeping peacefully.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought he hated Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know! It's because\NI look like Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why you don't like me,\nright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:30.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}weren't the eyes of hatred.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart is still pounding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:49.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}actually was in love\nwith Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must retrieve Kikyo's\nashes as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a dreadful feeling\nabout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's too late now, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you didn't want the ashes\nstolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,why didn't you just scatter\nthe ashes into the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You stayed sentimental and\nkept hanging on to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and see what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:20.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, how do you feel\nabout a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:25.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A grave is not simply a place\nto bury a body or ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:31.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A grave is necessary for the\nhearts of ones who are left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hearts of those left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister was born a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And she used her special powers\nfor the good of the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She kept demons\naway from the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and battled illness and\nfamine countless times...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,encouraging the people around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even after her demise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the villagers have not weakened,\nthey are resolved to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, man is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:05.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Danger and uncertainty can\nweaken his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The grave was a place\nof reassurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:13.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A place where hearts\ncould find peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm? Just like that time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is thinking\nof Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha was in love\nwith Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she shot an arrow\ninto him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he was bound for\nfifty years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel really sorry for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was unrequited love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unrequited love...\nunrequited love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with you, Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That look... gives me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you looking so sorry for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! I was thinking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... What were you thinking?!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:11.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:30.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see the result of my\nspecial magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kneading the earth from the grave\nwith the ashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and baking it in my Demon Kiln!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Looks quite good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:11.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arise! Open your eyes, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo... I have heard that as\na priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:46.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you foiled many an attempt\nby demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to possess the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I also hear that the Jewel is\nnow in fragments...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:56.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and a demon who possesses\neven one fragment of the Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,doubles its powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:04.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want it... I want every fragment\nof the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, you will go and destroy\nevery demon who seeks it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Burn and destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will serve me... the one who\nhas brought you back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will gather the fragments\nof the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh... W-what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A soul... The soul hasn't returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is no way my magic would\nfail to bring back the soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:57.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does this mean that the soul has\nalready been reincarnated...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in another body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:04.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then all I made was a hollow shape\nin the form of Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Making me work\nso hard and wasting my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:15.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Setting me up for failure like this!\NHow maddening!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't stand this! I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:27.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Earthen dolls? How creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to cross this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so scared!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go in and\ntalk some sense into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:48.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! I refuse to\nbe left behind on a bridge like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So come...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There're more of\nthe earthen dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soldiers of the\nold demoness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:11.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are the dolls we saw...\NIt can't be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, Old Woman...\NIt's gonna shake a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron Reaver Soul Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are these guys really\nmade of mud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Foxfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're not that strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just that they're so many of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the ruckus outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't stand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go out and work off\nthis frustration!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:53.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let go! This belongs\nto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does this mean?\NCould it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The resemblance!\NSuch a close resemblance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:18.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What coincidence!\NSuch good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That face... No mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:40.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny! Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:52.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I let go, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And now that I've found my\nreincarnated soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'd let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:03.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need you! In order to fully\nresurrect Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:07.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Resurrect... Kikyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo who died during the\NWarring States Era is resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:52.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the Sacred Jewel burst out\nof my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:56.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then perhaps, I really am the\nreincarnation of Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:59.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Urasue forces me to drink\na potion and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:01.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my soul is sucked out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo and Inuyasha's reunion\nafter fifty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rather than fond memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:07.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo still harbors a deep grudge\nand she goes after Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:13.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Return of the Tragic Priestess, Kikyo!"\NDon't miss it!
